{"type": "article", "id": 3906, "title": "Landscapes Within 系列家具", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-27T07:57:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233119UgaW08HJcsytexhv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t藤条制作的家具我们已经见多了，但是像波兰女设计师 Wiktoria Szawiel 设计的这一系列名为「Landscapes Within」却颠覆了我们惯常对藤制家具的理解，Landscapes Within 并不是以常见的编织藤条的方式制作而成，而是将藤条、柳条等材质与不同成分配比的树脂与石膏融合在一起，赋予了这一系列的椅子、边桌、凳子和餐具独一无二的视觉形象。Wiktoria Szawiel 希望能够用这些实实在在的物体来捕捉她曾经生长的地方的回忆。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233117uck7yTneZg2hqdix.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233117S6503MvhHVP4f7aD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233117n0y9zKd2hwva8LHF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233118nrCyTl31qZombEAj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233118GuPzdvBO9R4kZJF3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}